Body:
Description: Hello, got the 2 following errors when running the latest update.

(ERROR: 5 - Update Script checksum does not match the received checksum from Live Update Server)

Followed up with.

Some problems occurred during installation. Please Contact Support. (ERROR: 2 - Number of maximum retries for this update reached, skipping this update...)
What We've Learned Updated: The customer faced an error when they tried to apply the 5.9.4.1 server update while it was not available for download.
Next Steps Updated: The issue was addressed and I'm waiting for the customer to update the server and to confirm if the ticket can be closed.
